devdoc.details: Contract to manage a garage of cars for each user

addCar(string,string,string,uint256).details: Adds a new car to the caller's garage

params._numberOfDoors: The number of doors of the car

getMyCars().details: Retrieves the caller's array of cars

getUserCars(address).details: Retrieves a specific user's array of cars

resetMyGarage().details: Deletes all cars in the caller's garage

updateCar(uint256,string,string,string,u.details: Updates a specific car in the caller's garage

params._color: The new color of the car
params._index: The index of the car in the garage array
params._make: The new make of the car
params._model: The new model of the car
params._numberOfDoors: The new number of doors of the car
